&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Data Link (Layer 2)&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Packages data in frames appropriate to network transmission method&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Physical (Layer 1)&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Manages signaling to and from physical network connections&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
